## <a id="reqs"></a>Requirements

<%= vars.product_short %> has the following requirements:

* You must be signed up to and share Telemetry with Pivotal
* A Kubernetes cluster configured in [OIDC mode](https://docs.pivotal.io/pks/manage-cluster-permissions.html#cluster-access-user)
* A sandbox environment for testing

## <a id="limitations"></a>Limitations

### General Limitations

* This product is currently in alpha.
  * The structure of the product is fully subject to change in further alphas or later releases.
  * Pivotal does not provide commercial support for its alpha products.
* This product is intended to be used with any Kubernetes distribution. However, given the number of Kubernetes vendors, versions, and configurations, not all of them have been tested with PDC.
* Product upgrades are not supported. If you want to test a newer version, delete the previous version first.

